      "message": "[🟡 Suggestion] Line 137: An empty `originalBody` is used as both “no plugin overwrite” and “the real original body was empty”. That makes `EditedPopup.qml` and `isPluginOverwrite` unable to represent messages whose original body is intentionally empty and then overwritten by a plugin. Store explicit metadata for whether an overwrite exists, or preserve the original body separately without using emptiness as the sentinel.\n```suggestion\nstruct Body {\n    QString commitId;\n    QString body;\n    QString originalBody;\n    bool hasOriginalBody \u003d false;\n    std::time_t timestamp;\n};\n```",
